Pacotes Linux / Ubuntu

// - libdc1394 (1) 8.10
// > libdc1394/control/dc1394_control.h
// - libdc1394 (1) 9.04
// > libdc1394/dc1394_control.h
// - libdc1394 (2)
// > Pastas: dc1394/linux, dc1394/control, dc1394

// Ubuntu 8.04 / 8.10 : '/dev/video1394/0'
// Ubuntu 9.04 : '/dev/video1394-0'

===========================================================

Make sure you have firewire setup in your kernel

Install the libdc1394 library

